  stepNumber: 1
  stepText: "Welcome to Disc Pool \u2014 a fresh blend of Pool and Snooker rules,
    played with the flick mechanics of Carrom. \nInstead of balls, you\u2019ll be
    playing with discs, and instead of a cue ball, you\u2019ll use a striker. \nThe
    board is compact and rotates like a lazy-Susan, giving you full 360-degree control.
    \nThis is a brand-new experience in MR. Let\u2019s begin."
